data.description: Come to the established & highly desired Preserve at Alamo Ranch to see this immaculate home that is loaded with upgrades & charm. Fully landscaped in the front & backyard where you can enjoy beautiful flowers & over 19 mature oak trees for plenty of shade. Flagstone covered patio surrounded by stone & includes fireplace & outdoor kitchen. Inside the upgrades continue with hardwood floors throughout main living areas, study,& master bedroom. Plantation shutters through out & too many other features to name!
